# 3. Hardware Architecture

The system contains three major sections.

## Sensor Layer

The soil moisture sensor reads analog moisture values and sends them to ESP32.

## Control Layer

ESP32 processes sensor data and decides whether irrigation is needed.

## Actuation Layer

Relay controls the solenoid valve to allow or stop water flow.

## Dashboard Interface

The dashboard provides real-time visualization of telemetry and relay status.

