# 5. Firmware Features

## Automatic Irrigation

The ESP32 reads soil moisture continuously.

Logic:

* If soil value exceeds threshold → irrigation ON
* Otherwise → irrigation OFF

Threshold used:

```cpp
const int DRY_THRESHOLD = 2000;
```

## Manual Override

A physical push button toggles manual mode.

Manual mode behavior:

* Press button once → enable manual mode
* Press again → toggle valve state

## Serial Commands

### STATUS

Displays:

* Soil moisture percentage
* Pump/valve state
* Current mode

Example output:

```text
=== STATUS ===
Soil Moisture %: 51
Pump: ON
Mode: AUTO
```

### FORCE_ON

Forces valve ON.

### FORCE_OFF

Forces valve OFF.

## Web Server Control

Available endpoints:

```text
/on
/off
/status
```

## Telemetry Upload

Uploaded JSON:

```json
{
  "soil_moisture_pct": 52
}
```

Telemetry interval:

* Every 3 seconds

