# 9. Known Limitations

## Sensor Noise

Values may fluctuate near threshold.

## Relay Switching Delay

Mechanical relay adds delay.

## Button Debounce

Current debounce:

```cpp
delay(300);
```

## Wi-Fi Dependency

Telemetry stops without Wi-Fi.

## Security Limitation

Wi-Fi credentials are hardcoded.

